<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/434338-i-am-constantly-irritated-with-roger-and">I am constantly irritated with Roger and Brianna. Am I the only one? They are super tough characters for me.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_434338'><a id="like_count_community_question_434338" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/434338?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">104 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10967.The_Fiery_Cross">like</a></span>

</li>
