<span id="freeTextContainer11959194535168203955">Diana Jean Gabaldon Watkins grew up in Flagstaff, Arizona and is of Mexican-American and English descent. She has earned three degrees: a B.S. in Zoology, a M.S. in Marine Biology, and a Ph.D in Ecology.<br/><br/>She currently lives in Scottsdale, Arizona .</span>

